<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-white">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    
    <!-- Opening Section: Beyond Aid, A Framework for Change -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div class="container mx-auto flex px-5 py-24 items-center justify-center flex-col">
        <img class="lg:w-2/3 md:w-4/5 w-full mb-10 object-cover object-center rounded" alt="A Blueprint for Lasting Change" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=1200&h=400&fit=crop">
        <div class="text-center lg:w-2/3 w-full">
          <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">OUR STRATEGY FOR SUSTAINABLE IMPACT</h2>
          <h1 class="title-font sm:text-4xl text-3xl mb-4 font-medium text-gray-900">A Blueprint for Lasting Change</h1>
          <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">Humanitarian challenges are complex and interconnected. Delivering aid is critical, but it is not enough. At Peace and Humanitarian Initiatives, our work is guided by a holistic strategy designed to move communities from crisis and dependency to resilience and self-reliance. This framework ensures that every action we take contributes to a sustainable and peaceful future.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Guiding Philosophy Section -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font bg-blue-500">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-blue-500 mb-5 flex-shrink-0 mx-auto">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-10 h-10" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-100 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">OUR FOUNDATION</h2>
          <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-white">A Community-Centered Model</h1>
          <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base text-white">We believe that the most effective solutions come from the communities themselves. Our entire strategy is built on a participatory approach. We do not impose solutions; we partner with local communities, governments, and organizations to tailor every project to their unique needs and priorities. This focus on local ownership is the key to creating sustainable impact.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Strategic Pillars Section -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">THE CORE OF OUR WORK</h2>
          <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">Our Pillars of Action</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap -m-4">
          <div class="p-4 md:w-1/2">
            <div class="flex rounded-lg h-full bg-gray-100 p-8 flex-col">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 mr-3 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-500 text-white flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"></path>
                    <path d="M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-gray-900 text-lg title-font font-medium">Conflict Resolution & Peacebuilding</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-grow">
                <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">We facilitate dialogue, mediation, and community-driven peace education to address the root causes of conflict and foster reconciliation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 md:w-1/2">
            <div class="flex rounded-lg h-full bg-gray-100 p-8 flex-col">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 mr-3 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-500 text-white flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-gray-900 text-lg title-font font-medium">Humanitarian Relief & Resilience</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-grow">
                <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">We provide immediate, life-saving assistance while simultaneously building community-based systems for disaster risk reduction (DRR) and climate adaptation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 md:w-1/2">
            <div class="flex rounded-lg h-full bg-gray-100 p-8 flex-col">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 mr-3 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-500 text-white flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"></circle>
                    <circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"></circle>
                    <path d="M20 4L8.12 15.88M14.47 14.48L20 20M8.12 8.12L12 12"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-gray-900 text-lg title-font font-medium">Community & Youth Empowerment</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-grow">
                <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">We support long-term development through education, vocational training, micro-finance, and leadership programs that equip individuals to build self-reliant futures.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 md:w-1/2">
            <div class="flex rounded-lg h-full bg-gray-100 p-8 flex-col">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 mr-3 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-500 text-white flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-gray-900 text-lg title-font font-medium">Governance & Human Rights</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-grow">
                <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">We champion civil liberties, promote transparent and ethical governance, and advocate for the rights of marginalized groups to ensure a just and equitable society.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Principles of Execution Section -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">HOW WE ENSURE SUCCESS</h2>
          <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font text-gray-900">Our Commitment to Effective Implementation</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap">
          <div class="xl:w-1/3 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-500 mb-4">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Strategic Partnerships</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">We collaborate with local, national, and international organizations to leverage resources, expertise, and capacity. We build alliances with UN agencies, government bodies, and civil society to amplify our impact.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/3 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-500 mb-4">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Sustainability & Exit Strategy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">Every project is designed with the end in mind. We build the capacity of local stakeholders, hand over infrastructure to community committees, and integrate our work into district development plans to ensure continuity.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/3 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-500 mb-4">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Monitoring & Evaluation</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">We establish robust monitoring and evaluation systems for every project. Using SDG-aligned indicators and participatory feedback loops, we track progress, identify lessons learned, and remain accountable to our partners and the communities we serve.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final Call to Action -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">PARTNER WITH US</h2>
          <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">Invest in a Strategy, Not Just a Project</h1>
          <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base">Your support for PHI is an investment in a thoughtful, sustainable, and community-driven model for change. Partner with us to turn this strategic blueprint into life-changing action on the ground.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <a href="/initiatives.html" class="inline-flex text-white bg-blue-500 border-0 py-2 px-6 focus:outline-none hover:bg-blue-600 rounded text-lg">Explore Our Initiatives</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="ml-4 inline-flex text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 border-0 py-2 px-6 focus:outline-none hover:bg-gray-200 rounded text-lg">Contact Our Partnerships Team</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
